# REDUCE_FLAT -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_FLAT

=head1 AUTHORS

Frossie Economou <frossie@jach.hawaii.edu>
Paul Hirst <p.hirst@jach.hawaii.edu>

=head1 DESCIPTION

Reduces a flat field in the conventional manner, including
normalisation by polynomial fit. Files the normalised flat field frame
for use by subsequent flat fielding operations. 

=cut

_SPECTROSCOPY_HELLO_
_MASK_BAD_PIXELS_SPECT_
_SUBTRACT_BIAS_
#_SUBTRACT_DARK_SPECT_
_INTERLEAVE_DETECTOR_POSITIONS_
_COADD_MULTIPLE_EXPOSURES_
_NORMALIZE_FLAT_BY_POLY_
_FILE_FLAT_SPECT_
